            "jpText": "本気で悔しがるタマモクロス。\nそんな彼女を見たゴールドシチーは、自分が\nいかに周囲の声を意識していたか気づいた。",
            "enText": "Tamamo Cross was seriously frustrated. \nSeeing her like this, Gold City realized \nhow conscious she had been of the voices \naround her.",
