        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "自分の心の声を聞けていなかった。\nだが今は、純粋にレースに勝ちたい、\nもっと走りたいと心臓が叫んでいると話す。",
            "enText": "I wasn't listening to my heart. But \nnow, she says, her heart is screaming \nfor more running and she genuinely \nwants to win races.",
